Sentula Slides as Opencast Mining at Matadeni Halted While Talks Continue

-- B y   C a r l i   L o u r e n s
-- 
2011-03-31T08:16:27Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-31/sentula-slides-as-opencast-mining-at-matadeni-halted-while-talks-continue.html
Sentula Mining Ltd. declined in
Johannesburg trading after saying it halted mining at Matadeni
opencast section in  South Africa .  The stock declined 11 cents, or 3.8 percent, to 2.81 rand
as of 10:11 a.m. local time.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
